contentrichtext.text: '''Yass''' can refer to a number of things: * [[Catherine Yass]] - a painter. * [[Yass, New South Wales]] - a town in Australia. * [[Yass River]] - a river in the state of New South Wales, Australia. * [[Yass Valley Council]] - a local government area (shire) in New South Wales. * [[Yass (software)]] - a genomic local alignment tool. * [[Yass (music)]] - a style of [[Poland|Polish]] [[jazz music]] from the 1980s and 1990s. * [[Jass]] - a card game. * [[Yazz]] - a [[British people|British]] [[pop singer]] from the 1980s and 1990s. {{disambig}}
